{"tid":55003,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"賣走戴斯拿後，禾夫斯堡再有六將接近離隊？","createTime":"2016-12-26T04:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T07:28:07.000Z","uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"732971ea88b322195ecb4c8f3d6d7a80612e3ca3","tid":55003,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:56:33.000Z","msg":"來自德國《圖片報》的消息，在成功賣走德國中場戴斯拿後，禾夫斯堡更計劃進行一輪的大清洗，其中6名球員或將相繼轉會。<br />\n<br />\n不久前，禾夫斯堡前鋒馬里奧高美斯曾指出，一些不希望繼續留隊的球員，應該被清洗，而事實上，狼堡目前的軍心相當不穩，皆因多名球員均展現離心。除了戴斯拿之外，盛傳有6名禾夫斯堡球員同樣可能面臨離隊。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這6名球員包括古斯達禾、列卡度洛迪古斯、卡斯迪爾斯、禾爾舒捷特、韋連拿和阿斯古斯，其中古斯達禾和列卡度洛迪古斯極有可能於今冬，一同轉投意甲豪門國際米蘭。<br />\n<br />\n抵啦 賣巴斯杜斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf816589bca1dccaaf187c694e307ec39e357bc","tid":55003,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T04:57:04.000Z","msg":"執柒佢啦😅"},{"pid":"e4e41af1788831fd90c2358045f18a7686ceebdc","tid":55003,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:08:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>執柒佢啦😅</blockquote><br />\nyes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成隊波冇咗N賓之後冇場好波"},{"pid":"833cdc26eb077bc4d6bdfc18e79327ee028ef197","tid":55003,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>執柒佢啦😅</blockquote><br />\nyes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成隊波冇咗N賓之後冇場好波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nN賓/dos&gt;迪布尼"},{"pid":"f9f501e2e1ff1d9c352a789d7178fc394e0bc297","tid":55003,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:17:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>執柒佢啦😅</blockquote><br />\nyes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成隊波冇咗N賓之後冇場好波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nN賓/dos&gt;迪布尼</blockquote><br />\nyes<br />\n蓋清&gt;泥清"},{"pid":"674d9030368c2adc157c0e931632419f07577b03","tid":55003,"uid":30768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor